#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/datetime.md:3
msgid ""
"Date and time helpers are available under `ptool.datetime` and `p.datetime`."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/datetime.md:5
msgid ""
"`ptool.datetime` works with concrete instants. Every `DateTime` value "
"carries a timezone or numeric offset."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/datetime.md:8
msgid "ptool.datetime.now"
msgstr ""

